<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="203" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1127,1278,1462]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,243,1278,1302]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Biology.</emphasis>
Adults: wingspan 
<quantity box="[439,551,1278,1302]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" metricValueMax="2.4" metricValueMin="1.9" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" unit="mm" value="21.5" valueMax="24.0" valueMin="19.0">19-24 mm</quantity>
. The adults fly from April to September, reaching up to 
<quantity box="[151,239,1310,1334]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" unit="m" value="2.0">2,000 m</quantity>
a.s.l. In north-eastern 
<collectingRegion box="[477,539,1310,1334]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Sicily</collectingRegion>
it has been observed only in May. Our specimens were captured at dusk while flying over the grass in a field near a rocky habitat. Larval host plant: probably monophagous on 
<taxonomicName box="[442,658,1375,1398]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Saxifragaceae" genus="Saxifraga" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="granulata">
<emphasis box="[442,658,1375,1398]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Saxifraga granulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. (
<taxonomicName box="[701,857,1374,1398]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Saxifragaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Saxifragaceae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1127,1278,1462]" box="[151,1008,1406,1430]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,318,1406,1430]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">
Range in 
<collectingCountry box="[259,313,1406,1430]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Italy</collectingCountry>
.
</emphasis>
Northern and central parts of the peninsula; 
<collectingRegion box="[795,857,1406,1430]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Sicily</collectingRegion>
(new record).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
